    "Process transparency can be bolstered by auditability, monitoring, and adoption of open-source development practices.",
    "Although interpretability and explainability remain burgeoning research areas, there is a diverse range of methods for attaining these goals, each suitable for specific contexts.",
    "The promotion of ethics in health care on SMPs involves the use of simulation, modeling, data analytics, sentiment analysis, crowdsourcing, and automated systems considering both professional and social ethics.",
